Thoughts on email and SMS integration
======================================

Emails: emails are essential for any kind of communication such as
	1. User foun some information on our product and he wants to send that link to self or to anyone
	2. Registration confirmation
	3. Any updates/notifications
	4. Leave plan
	5. Trip plans

SMS: 
	1. Can be used for validating user identity
	2. Registration confirmation
	3. For updates/notifications
	4. SMS support for data update on the fly
	5. 
